{"file_name": "Accountant_multipage.pdf", "file_type": "pdf", "confidence": 0.78, "time_taken": 0.92, "memory_mb": 5.14, "units": [{"index": 1, "method": "structured", "confidence": 0.79, "text": {"text": "JOHN DOE\nSenior Accountant\nMumbai, India | john.doe@email.com | +91-9XXXXXXXXX\nPROFESSIONAL SUMMARY\nSenior Accountant with over 12 years of experience in financial accounting, auditing, taxation, and regulatory\ncompliance across manufacturing, IT, and professional services industries. Proven expertise in managing\nend-to-end accounting operations, ensuring statutory compliance, and delivering accurate financial insights to\nsenior leadership. Strong analytical mindset with a track record of improving reporting accuracy, optimizing costs,\nand strengthening internal controls.\nCORE COMPETENCIES\n(cid:127) Financial Accounting & Reporting\n(cid:127) Statutory & Internal Audits\n(cid:127) Taxation (GST, TDS, Income Tax)\n(cid:127) Budgeting & Forecasting\n(cid:127) Cost Control & Variance Analysis\n(cid:127) Internal Controls & Compliance\n(cid:127) ERP Systems: SAP, Oracle, Tally\n(cid:127) Advanced Excel & Financial Modelling\nPROFESSIONAL EXPERIENCE\nSenior Accountant \u2013 ABC Finance Ltd (2018 \u2013 Present)\n(cid:127) Lead end-to-end accounting operations for a mid-sized organization with annual turnover exceeding INR 250\nCrores.\n(cid:127) Prepare and review monthly, quarterly, and annual financial statements in compliance with IND-AS and statutory\nrequirements.\n(cid:127) Coordinate with external auditors and successfully closed audits with zero major observations for four\nconsecutive years.\n(cid:127) Implemented automated reconciliation processes, reducing month-end close time by 25%.\n(cid:127) Partner with senior management to support strategic decision-making through detailed financial analysis and\nMIS reporting.", "tables": []}}, {"index": 2, "method": "structured", "confidence": 0.77, "text": {"text": "Accountant \u2013 XYZ Professional Services (2012 \u2013 2018)\n(cid:127) Managed day-to-day accounting operations including accounts payable, accounts receivable, and general ledger\nmaintenance.\n(cid:127) Prepared balance sheets, profit & loss statements, and cash flow statements for multiple client accounts.\n(cid:127) Independently handled GST registration, filings, and reconciliations for over 20 clients across different industries.\n(cid:127) Assisted in income tax assessments and successfully resolved departmental queries with supporting\ndocumentation.\n(cid:127) Improved billing accuracy and reduced revenue leakage by 15% through process standardization.\nKEY ACHIEVEMENTS\n(cid:127) Reduced audit observations by 40% through strengthened internal controls.\n(cid:127) Identified cost-saving opportunities resulting in annual savings of INR 18 Lakhs.\n(cid:127) Recognized as \u201cBest Performer \u2013 Finance\u201d for two consecutive years.\nEDUCATION\n(cid:127) Chartered Accountant (CA) \u2013 Institute of Chartered Accountants of India (ICAI)\n(cid:127) Bachelor of Commerce (B.Com) \u2013 University of Mumbai\nCERTIFICATIONS\n(cid:127) Certified GST Practitioner\n(cid:127) Diploma in IFRS\nADDITIONAL INFORMATION\n(cid:127) Strong communication and stakeholder management skills\n(cid:127) Experience working with cross-functional teams\n(cid:127) Willingness to adapt to evolving regulatory environments", "tables": []}}], "error": null, "embedding": [0.012285853736102581, 0.027122236788272858, -0.006375148426741362, -0.00600457563996315, 0.040236517786979675, 0.0018167898524552584, 0.010750946588814259, 0.032579634338617325, -0.0037000204902142286, -0.0054613440297544, -0.002626259345561266, -0.01602354273200035, -0.02210056036710739, 0.012582783587276936, 0.042572230100631714, 0.05178803205490112, 0.03126172721385956, 0.01709161326289177, 0.05264973267912865, -0.04325556382536888, 0.00867976900190115, -0.018210962414741516, -0.00960435438901186, 0.0554424412548542, 0.012397194281220436, 0.0169957